<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-462] bad normalization in sorted search returning TopDocs</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-462</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;FieldSortedHitQueue.maxscore is maintained in the lessThan method (which never gets called if a single document is added to the queue).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve checked in a test to TestSort.testTopDocsScores() with the final assertion commented out.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
